From: David Cook <divergentdave@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 7 Nov 2020 10:12:44 -0600
Subject: Check for arithmetic overflows before allocating
Origin: https://github.com/p11-glue/p11-kit/commit/commit/5307a1d21a50cacd06f471a873a018d23ba4b963
Bug: https://github.com/p11-glue/p11-kit/security/advisories/GHSA-q4r3-hm6m-mvc2
Bug-Debian-Security: https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2020-29361
[Salvatore Bonaccorso: Backport to 0.23.15 (context changes)]

---
 p11-kit/iter.c        |  4 ++--
 p11-kit/lists.c       |  2 ++
 p11-kit/proxy.c       |  2 +-
 p11-kit/rpc-message.c | 13 +++++++++++++
 p11-kit/rpc-message.h |  4 ++++
 p11-kit/rpc-server.c  |  8 ++++----
